✅📖 Surah Al-Fatiha – Tafseer aur Ta‘aruf 🌿

🌸 Ta‘aruf :-

📖 Surah Al-Fatiha Qur’an ki pehli Surah hai.
🔢 Isme 7 ayaat hain.
🕌 Isay har rakat mein padhna farz hai, isliye isko “Surah as-Salah” bhi kehte hain.
🤲 Yeh ek dua hai jo banda Allah se karta hai.
🌸 Surah Al-Fatiha ko Umm al-Qur’an (Qur’an ki maa) kehte hain.
✨ Yeh dua aur hamd dono hai:
           🌿 Hamd (tareef aur shukr Allah ka)
           🌙 Dua (seedhe raaste ki hidayat maangna)
🌟 Qur’an ka asal paigham isi Surah mein condensed hai.

______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________


📖 Tafseer (Ayaat by Ayaat):-

                                      🌸 Bismillāhir-Raḥmānir-Raḥīm  🌸
                                          بِسْمِ اللّٰهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِ
                        “In the name of Allah, the Most Gracious, the Most Merciful.”
                              "Allah ke naam se jo nihāyat Meharbān, Raḥīm hai."

1️⃣ Alhamdu lillahi Rabbil-‘aalameen
👉 Saari tareef Allah ke liye hai jo tamaam jahanon ka Rab hai.
🌿 Rabb matlab: paida karne wala, paalne wala, parwarish karne wala.
🌍 Allah sab insaan, jinn, farishte, pauday, janwar sab ka Rab hai.
💡 Lesson: Har ni’mat Allah se hai, shukr usi ka karna hai.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

2️⃣ Ar-Rahmaanir-Raheem
👉 Jo bohot mehrbaan, nihayat reham karne wala hai.
🌸 Rahmaan: sab par aam rehmat (momineen aur ghair momin dono par).
✨ Raheem: khaas rehmat momineen ke liye akhirat mein.
💡 Lesson: Allah ki rehmat se kabhi mayoos na ho.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

3️⃣ Maaliki Yawmid-Deen
👉 Qiyamat ke din ka asal Malik.
⚖️ Us din na maal chalega, na rishtedari, sirf aamaal ka hisaab hoga.
💡 Lesson: Zindagi akhirat ki tayyari ke liye guzarna chahiye.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

4️⃣ Iyyaka na‘budu wa iyyaka nasta‘een
👉 Sirf teri ibadat aur sirf tujh se madad.
🕋 Tawheed ka paigham — ibadat sirf Allah ki.
🤲 Har mushkil mein asal madadgar Allah.
💡 Lesson: Ikhlaas aur Tawheed har amal mein.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

5️⃣ Ihdinas-Siraatal-Mustaqeem
👉 Hume seedha raasta dikha.
🛤️ Hidayat sirf Allah deta hai.
🌟 Nabi ﷺ aur sahaba ka raasta hi asal seedha raasta hai.
💡 Lesson: Roz hidayat ki dua karna.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

6️⃣ Siraatal-lazeena an‘amta ‘alayhim
👉 Jin par tu ne in‘aam kiya unka raasta.
✨ In‘aam wale: Ambiya, Siddiqeen, Shuhada, Saleheen.
💡 Lesson: Achhe role models aur sohbat chuno.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

7️⃣ Ghayril-maghdoobi ‘alayhim walad-daaalleen
👉 Na gusse walon ka raasta, na bhatke huon ka.
⚡ Maghdoob: Yahood (jin par gussa hua).
🚫 Daalleen: Nasara (jo bhatak gaye).
💡 Lesson: Gumrahi aur ghalat raaston se bachna.

______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌟 Asal Paigham (Main Messages) ;-
🌍 Allah sab jahanon ka Rab hai.
🌸 Allah ki sabse badi sifaat uski rehmat hai.
⚖️ Qiyamat ka din haq hai.
🕋 Sirf Allah ki ibadat aur usi se madad.
🛤️ Roz Allah se hidayat maangna.
✨ Saleheen aur Ambiya ke raaste par chalna.
🚫 Gumrahi aur gusse wale raaston se bachna.

______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌼 Extra Points
🕋 Surah Fatiha ek dialogue hai Allah aur banda ke darmiyan 
    (Hadith Qudsi: “Maine apne bande aur apne darmiyan Surah Fatiha ko do hisson mein taqseem kiya hai”).
📖 Yeh Surah poore Qur’an ka summary hai.
🤲 Yeh hume dua seekhati hai — har ibadat ke baad Allah se hidayat maangna.
🌟 Isme Tawheed, Akhirat, Ibadat aur Risalah sab cover hai.

______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________ 

✨ Life Lessons
🌸 Har amal ki ibtida Bismillah aur Alhamdulillah se karna.
❤️ Hamesha rehmat aur shafqat apnana.
⚖️ Apni zindagi akhirat ke hisaab ke liye tayyar karna.
🕋 Sirf Allah ki ibadat aur ikhlaas.
🤲 Roz hidayat ki dua karna.
🌿 Saleheen ki sohbat aur unke tareeqe par chalna.
🚫 Gumrahi aur nafrat ke raste se door rehna.
